title: ✨ Great price 1x1 available this month! ✨
posting_body: ['🔑 TRAMOR HUNTERS GLEN 🔑', '*If you sign up with our preferred renters insurance provider, ePremium, we can waive $100 off the security deposit, as well as waive the $200 pet deposits if you have pets!', '🐾 Mention this ad!*', 'APARTMENT FEATURES', 'Pictures are of actual unit - available NOW', 'You will have 496 sqft and a covered patio!', 'The unit is located on the first floor and is going for $1250/month.', "The apartment is Google Fiber-ready with a jack, but if you'd like to opt for a different provider feel free!", 'Water is allocated (usually about $35/person) and electricity is set up through the City of Austin!', 'Only $1/wash and $1/dry at our 24/7 on-site laundry facility!', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '- No breed restrictions/weight limits', '- Courtyard areas', '- Swimming pool', '- Property security', '- Near transportation + very walkable!', '- Laundry Facility on site', '- 24/7 maintenance', '- Guest parking', '- Off-street parking', 'Private and tucked away location!', 'Contact info:', 'Abi', 'Tramor Hunters Glen']
